    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>General term for relatively large areas, usually named but having undefined boundaries, where ancient cultures existed. For ancient administrative areas that are defined by historical boundaries, use "former primary political entities" or "former administrative divisions."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
